games.description: Just Slap It is a fun and lighthearted slap-based game where timing and accuracy are key. Compete in slap battles, perfect your timing, and climb the leaderboard to showcase your skills. With simple controls and engaging gameplay, challenge yourself to out-slap opponents and rise to the top. Unlock upgrades and enjoy quick, casual fun anytime.
games.instructions: Just click/tap on screen to slap!

games.description: Step into the thrilling world of Squid Game Memory Card Match! Test your memory and focus as you uncover pairs of iconic Squid Game symbols and characters. Can you keep your cool under pressure and match all the cards before time runs out? Challenge yourself or compete with friends to see who can master the ultimate memory test. With Squid Game Memory Card Match, every flip brings you closer to victory or defeat – can you handle the pressure?
games.instructions: Mouse Click

games.description: In Traffic Jam: Hop On, challenge your strategy thinking and quick reflexes! This wonderful puzzle game will take you into a colorful parking lot. Your task is to help all kinds of vehicles get out of traffic jams and start smoothly.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Welcome to the world of Car Derby Arena! In this exciting game you can enjoy the unique experience of changing the color of cars, improving their performance, and manipulating gravity and weather conditions. Your goal is to become an invincible master of destruction, pump up your car and crush everything in your path. Embark on exciting missions, compete with other players and prove your skills in this epic Car Derby Arena game!
games.instructions: PC control: WASD or arrows - drive. C - change camera. R - repair the car. F - nitro acceleration. P - pause game. Spacebar - handbrake. F2 - restart the level. G - open and close the gravity panel, slow down time. Keys 1 through 9 to switch the level of gravity, as well as the keys 0 and "-".

games.description: “Dead Brain” puts you in the shoes of a fearless farmer standing between your crops and the undead hordes. With simple controls and intense action, players must strategically use random upgrades to survive each wave and push their limits. After each victorious wave, you'll get to choose a random bonus to aid your survival. Gain a new weapon, heal your hero, repair your defenses, or even boost your health! Are you ready to defend your farm and become the ultimate zombie-slaying hero?
games.instructions: Use your mouse to aim and shoot enimies.

games.description: This is a collection of creative and fun mini-games. The game contains a variety of modes, you can DIY ice cream, have cooking for mooncakes, design a car of your favorite, and so on. You cant miss our game if you want to find some relaxation in your busy life.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Cop Simulator is an exciting and dynamic gaming experience that immerses you in the world of a lawman with unlimited possibilities. In this game you will take on the role of a cop, where you are given complete freedom of action.
games.instructions: Controls on the desktop - WASD for movement, Mouse for viewing, Space for jumping, C for crouching, F for interacting with cars. Control on a mobile device - touch/swipe.

games.description: Survive the zombie apocalypse in this fast-paced 2D top-down tower defense game. Construct and upgrade various defensive turrets to take down hordes of undead attackers. Earn coins by killing zombies and use them to purchase new towers, upgrade existing ones, or sell for cash and reinvest into a different turret. Defend your base from waves of shambling corpses as you fight to stay alive in a world gone mad.
games.instructions: Construct defensive turrets. Stop the zombie horde from reaching your base.

games.description: Sorting Balls is a fun and challenging puzzle game where players must sort colored balls into the correct tubes. The goal is to organize all the balls by color using logical thinking and strategic moves. As the levels progress, the puzzles become more complex, requiring careful planning. With simple controls and engaging mechanics, Sorting Balls is perfect for players who enjoy brain-teasing challenges.
games.instructions: 1. Tap a tube to pick up the top ball. 2. Tap another tube to place the ball if it matches the top color or if the tube is empty. 3. Continue sorting until all balls are grouped by color. 4. Plan your moves carefully—some levels require strategy! 5. Complete the level to progress to more challenging puzzles.

games.description: Dive into the enchanting world of Bloom Sort 2: Bee Puzzle, where flowers bloom, bees buzz, and your mind gets a delightful workout! This unique 3D puzzle game combines stunning 2D and 3D graphics with a relaxing, chill vibe, making it the perfect escape for players of all ages.
games.instructions: Embark on an endless adventure of sorting, matching, and blooming flowers in a garden. Experience the joy of connecting colorful flowers and creating beautiful patterns while you unwind from the stresses of everyday life.

games.description: Squid Challenge: Play to Survive is an intense survival game inspired by the thrilling challenges of the popular survival contest. Players must navigate through a series of deadly trials, testing their reflexes, strategy, and nerve. With each level, the difficulty increases, making it a true test of skill and endurance.
games.instructions: Survive all the dangerous challenges and progress through the rounds. Follow the game’s rules strictly—one mistake can mean elimination. Complete each task within the given time limit to advance. Controls: Tap or Swipe: Interact with objects and move your character. Hold & Release: Stop when required in "Red Light, Green Light." Button Mashing: Use rapid taps for strength-based challenges like Tug of War.

games.description: Master programming logic with Code Maze! Use code blocks to navigate mazes, overcome obstacles, and reach goals. Each level challenges your problem-solving skills. Ready to code your way out?
games.instructions: Drag code blocks to guide your avatar through the maze. Use moves, loops, and conditionals to reach the goal efficiently. Fewer blocks mean higher scores. Test, retry, and conquer each level!

games.description: Pixel Path is a platformer with a non—standard plot.? Get to the portal at the end of the level to win, but it's not as easy as it might seem... The floor may collapse, the spikes will move on you, and your character will grow to huge sizes. One wrong step and the game is over.❌ You will have to keep your sanity, expect surprises, show a good reaction and most importantly: do not get angry.? The game also has a table of the best players who completed all levels faster than the rest.
games.instructions: The goal is simple: get to the portal at the end of the level, the path to it is not as easy as it may seem... Movement - arrow buttons or W A S D. On computer: view rewarded ads when they are available - G. Exit to menu - ESC.

games.description: Epic Car Stunt Race Obby is a fast-paced, acrobatic and challenging stunt racing game. In these races with hundreds of different levels, each new track creates a completely different excitement with its special design. You can play Epic Car Stunt Race Obby against AI racers or with your friend in 2 player mode. Start the endless racing excitement now!
games.instructions: PLAYER 1 Movement: "W,A,S;D" (Arrow keys are also active in 1 Player mode.) Nitro: "SHIFT" Respawn: "R" Camera: "C" PLAYER 2 Movement: "ARROW KEYS" Nitro: "N" Respawn: "U" Camera: "L"

games.description: We are glad to welcome you to the bright world of a humorous dress-up game where fashion collides with the comic book universe! Get ready for a creative reinterpretation of your favorite comic book anti-hero costumes: bold color combinations, unexpected prints and fun accessories are available to you. There is everything here: from funny hats that emphasize individuality to stylish superhero jumpsuits. Unleash your imagination!
games.instructions: Let's mentally jump into the comic book universe to create a vibrant and unusual female version of our favorite anti-hero. Successful images can be saved as PNG images. Depending on the gaming device, a computer mouse click or a simple touch on touch screens is used to control it.

games.description: Cannon Shooter is an exciting arcade shooter where you can have endless shooting fun in fast-paced combat! You will control a cannonball firing hordes of heroic characters, facing many enemies. A quick click to launch more heroes and help you generate more heroes through the digital gate.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Listen to the voices and enjoy the visuals of the Brawl Stars characters. Start your sound-filled brawling adventure and enjoy a unique auditory twist in your gaming routine!
games.instructions: Press the buttons of different characters to hear unique sounds and see exciting visual effects appear!

games.description: Block Up Contrast is a minimalist arcade game where you need a moving block upward through an endless series of obstacles. The challenge is to avoid barriers of contrasting colors while collecting points. The game requires precise timing and quick reflexes as the speed increases. With simple yet engaging gameplay, Block Up Contrast offers an addictive experience for players.
games.instructions: 1. Tap to move the block upward. 2. Avoid obstacles of contrasting colors. 3. Time your taps carefully to navigate through gaps. 4. Collect points to increase your score. 5. React quickly as the speed increases over time.

games.description: Traffic Tap Puzzle is a challenging puzzle game where players must control traffic at intersections by tapping on cars to start or stop them. The goal is to avoid collisions while ensuring a smooth flow of vehicles. As the levels progress, traffic becomes more complex, requiring strategic timing and quick decision-making. With engaging mechanics and increasing difficulty, the game tests your reflexes and planning skills.
games.instructions: Tap on a car to make it move or stop. Time your taps carefully to prevent crashes. Let all cars pass safely to complete the level. The difficulty increases with more cars and faster movement. Plan ahead and react quickly to manage traffic efficiently.

games.description: "Doggo Jump" is a charming hyper-casual platform game where players controls a playful puppy as it hops between platforms, collecting bones and racking up points. With simple tap-to-jump mechanics, colorful graphics, and an adorable dog character, the game is easy to pick up and addictive, making it perfect for quick gaming sessions.
games.instructions: Tap anywhere to make the Doggo fall faster

games.description: Pool 8 is a relaxing yet challenging billiards-style puzzle game where players must sink all the balls into the pockets in the correct order. The game follows a step-by-step movement system, requiring strategic planning to clear the table efficiently. With smooth mechanics and progressively difficult levels, Pool 8 offers a unique twist on classic pool gameplay, perfect for puzzle and strategy lovers.
games.instructions: 1. Swipe to move the cue ball in a straight line. 2. Plan your moves carefully—balls can only be pocketed in a specific order. 3. Use walls to change direction if necessary. 4. Clear the table by sinking all balls correctly. 5. Think ahead and strategize to complete each level efficiently!

games.description: This game is extremely more difficult and filled with challenges compared to the previous one. You need to become Huggy and catch all your clones. Catch all the clones and hunt them down, but remember, some of them must be thrown out of the maze. No one should see you, and you must not get caught while hunting someone. Be very careful, the clones are everywhere and extremely dangerous. Some doors can only be opened by you. Open the doors and hunt the clones.
games.instructions: *Use the "arrow keys" to move. *Press the "Space" key to kill someone. *Playable on both mobile and PC. *Collect energy boxes, extend the mission time.

games.description: Disk Rush is a reaction-based arcade game where players must quickly sort colored disks into their matching zones. The game challenges your speed and accuracy as disks appear faster over time. With simple tap mechanics and increasing difficulty, Disk Rush tests your ability to think and act quickly under pressure.
games.instructions: 1. Watch the color of the incoming disk. 2. Tap the correct side of the screen to send it to the matching zone. 3. Be quick—disks appear faster as the game progresses! 4. Sorting incorrectly ends the game, so stay focused. 5. Keep playing to beat your high score!

game_info.title: Find It In The Haunted Mansion

games.description: “Find It In The Haunted Mansion” is a finding style game, where you are a detective and need to find all the keys hidden in each part of the house to complete all the levels.
games.instructions: On mobile, use screen touch On the computer, use the mouse.

games.description: Yoga Master - Flex Running is an addictive 3D running game with different levels that will challenge even the fastest reflex. Move your character to adjust the pose and dodge the incoming obstacles while picking some money on the way. But beware! Sometimes this stack of cash is a trap.
games.instructions: HOW TO PLAY: - Tap or swipe to begin a level. - Swipe to move the character. - Adjust the pose to dodge the furniture. - Don't let anything hit you until the end.

games.description: Enter the world of Mystical Blades, where you design and battle your own B-Blades! Mix blades, rings, and elements to create powerful combos, then face players worldwide in thrilling battles. With stunning graphics and realistic physics, prove your skills and become the ultimate B-Blades master!
games.instructions: Use the mouse or touchscreen to play the game.

games.description: Challenging yet relaxing Nuts & Bolts sort puzzle with a unique twist! Nuts Stack Sort: Nuts & Bolts is a fun and addictive stack sort puzzle game with a unique twist! Strategically sort and match three same color nuts based on box color in this jam puzzles. Every level offers an exciting challenge in this addictive sort colors puzzle game. Test yourself with this amazing brain teaser!
games.instructions: Easy tap and match mechanic. Tap and sort nuts according to box color.

games.description: Test your strategy and speed in Shelf Shift Match! Shift items on the shelves to create perfect matches of three, clearing the way to reveal hidden shadowed items. But beware—unwise moves can block your shelves, leaving no space to shift and leading to game over! If you're stuck, use the shuffle button to mix things up and find new matches.
games.instructions: Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game.

games.description: Flow Lines is an engaging and straightforward puzzle game where the main objective is to connect dots of the same color through a continuous path on a grid.
games.instructions: To play Flow Lines, tap on a colored dot and drag your finger across the screen to create a path connecting it to another dot of the same color. Ensure that the lines are continuous and do not overlap. The goal is to fill every square on the grid without

games.description: Police Chase Drifter is a fun car game where you get to run from the police, collect money bags and reach to the finishline. Earn money to buy more cars, fasters and enjoy the drifting.
games.instructions: Arrow keys and WSAD to accelerate, brakes and steer.

games.description: Doodle Football is an imaginative and captivating 2D casual game that combines creativity, strategy, and fun. Your goal is simple: guide the football into the goal while overcoming exciting challenges across a variety of themes like the lush greenery of fields, the scorching sands of the desert, and the frosty landscapes of ice.
games.instructions: Left mouse button to draw a line. Restart button or R to restart. Start button or Space to start. [Use Landscape mode for Mobile devices]

games.description: Winter has come, and the snowfall has begun. Since it's Christmas time, the wolf must find three stars during the winter. The wolf needs to carefully hunt and catch three sheep, take their stars, and gather all the bones on the path to avoid starving. It must also be cautious of the hunters in the forest. At the end of the level, it must reach the dark portal to teleport to its desired location.
games.instructions: *Use the "WASD" keys to move. *Double Jump is active. *Collect all 3 stars and bones to activate the dark portal.

games.description: Use your buddies to take down the enemy structures and the enemies along with them! Can you make survive the hero? Use the physics of the world to skillfully take down Sam's enemies!
games.instructions: Drag to Aim, Release to shoot

games.description: Welcome to ultimate strategy game that lets you improve your tactical skills and lead your troops to triumph! Lead your army, conquer enemy camps, and expand your territory in fast-paced battles filled with action and strategy. Every decision matters — whether you’re attacking enemy strongholds or defending your bases, clever maneuvers are key to achieving victory.
games.instructions: Drag your troops with your mouse/finger to the building you want to occupy. Occupy all enemy buildings to win.

games.description: Jump, Place Blocks, and Conquer Challenging Levels! In Air Block, use quick reflexes and smart block placement to overcome obstacles and enemies. With limited blocks per level, every move counts! Avoid saws, spikes, and unlock doors to progress—plus, grab those bananas if you can! Game Modes: Single Player – Test your skills across unique levels. Two-Player Mode – Compete in quick place challenges and mini-games like Beach Ball, with more to come! Think you’ve got what it takes? Start now!
games.instructions: 1st Player Controls : A, W, D -> Move, Space -> Place blocks 2nd Player Controls: Up, Left, Right arrow keys -> Move, Left Mouse Click -> Place Blocks Tip: First Jump, Release the Jump Key and then Place the Blocks!

games.description: You run and you shoot. That’s all you do, but this deceptively simple game mixes up the action and racks up the adrenalin with surprises round every corner to ensure you never get bored. Trigger finger itchy?
games.instructions: You’ll need to have all your wits about you and pistols at the ready to keep on running ? and keep on gunning. Enemies appear on all sides, and you have to take them down before they open fire on you to survive. Use explosives, extinguishers, and utility pipes to deal extra damage and take out multiple enemies with a single shot. Just make sure you don’t hit the innocent civilians you were sent here to save!

games.description: Explore action-packed mini-games, customize your hero, and test your skills in fun challenges. Whether you enjoy racing, creativity, or exciting adventures, this app has everything you need for endless fun!
games.instructions: Bottle Smash: tap or click to shoot Skateboarding Rush: buttons on screen for jump and sit Car Racing: swipe left or right to move Web Swinging: tap to shoot web, button on screen to let go of the web Fishing Frenzy: Buttons on screen for throw hook and pull the reel Wall Climber: swipe left or right to move Creative Studio: draw with the tools on the screen

games.description: The dynamic gun runner game gives a shooting experience with the creation and evolution of weapons. Combine parts to get new weapon modules. Shoot obstacles and enemies to unlock an arsenal of powerful weapons. Test your marksmanship by shooting at targets and enemies. Improve your firepower by creating and combining weapon parts. Follow the evolution of weapons, from simple firearms to advanced weaponry. Become a true master of weapon creation!
games.instructions: Use your mouse to move around on PC and your finger on your phone. To upgrade weapons, you need to buy and connect parts.

games.description: Transform into the ultimate spider in Spider Evolution! Start small, grow stronger, and outsmart rivals on a vibrant track. Merge, dodge, and strategize to become the apex arachnid. Experience thrilling hyper-casual gameplay and dominate the spider world!
games.instructions: Keyboard arrow keys or A D keys to control player to move left or right, or use mouse control with right slider or left slide.

games.description: You need to escape from the Squid competition, but while running away, you fell into the Block world. It’s a bit hard to escape from the Block world, but don’t stop and keep running. Never stop running until you reach the purple portal. Don’t forget to collect the money you see on the way. Be careful of the big monsters chasing you from behind; they want to catch you, and if they do, you’ll lose.
games.instructions: *Use the 'WASD' and 'Arrow keys' to move. *To survive, run to the portal at the end of the level and be careful of obstacles.

games.description: In Bang Bang Mahjong, we mix classic Mahjong with a sliding puzzle twist. It might seem simple at first, but as the levels get trickier, every move counts. Move the tiles around and match identical ones. Power-ups like shuffle, remove, or hints can help when things get tough. With each completed level, the challenge grows—but so does the satisfaction of solving it. Who can master every puzzle and clear the board like a pro?
games.instructions: Use the mouse or finger to move tiles around to align identical patterns, clearing them from the board.

games.description: Before the sprunks take on their immediate duties, namely creating music, you must unlock sixteen characters. In the meantime, you have no one to create your own melodies with. To bring the Sprunki back to life, you must collect an image of each Sprunki. The picture consists of nine square fragments that are mixed on the playing field. Swap them and install them in the correct positions. Having collected all the puzzles, you can start making music in Sprunki Puzzles and Singing.
games.instructions: Use your mouse or tap the screen.

games.description: This is an ASMR game for girls. If you like to clean everything, our game is right for you. The game has 5 modes: ear cleaning, heel cleaning, back spa, teeth cleaning, and fan cleaning. You can use different tools to clean and massage your body parts. But it is important to note that each mode has a countdown time and you must choose the right tool to do the cleaning.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: The city is under attack by dangerous zombies, and you must become a hero to save it! Awakened by a dream, you take on the mantle of a human warrior with unlimited potential, joining other survivors to fight against the evil horde. But with the zombies greatly outnumbering you, any mistake could lead to dire consequences. You must find a way to survive this crisis.
games.instructions: Just run and gun!

games.description: You have to play as a Stickman astronaut who is stuck on the moon. Use all possible ways to leave the moon and get to our planet Earth. On the way you will encounter various dangers, such as aliens, flying meteorites and much more. You will have several objects in your hands with which you can try to escape from the natural satellite of the moon. Several objects will lead you to death, and some objects can save your life, be careful and cautious.
games.instructions: Find two successful ways to escape from the Moon. Use your computer mouse to control the game. If you have a mobile device, use a stylus or your finger.

games.description: Fire off your epic selection of awesome guns to reach the end of each level while causing chaos and destruction! Amass coins to unlock more guns across endless levels of utter carnage!!!!! (╯°□°）╯︵ ┻━┻
games.instructions: Simply tap, click or press enter to shoot and move in the opposite direction you fire!

games.description: When a mysterious radiation blast grants Stickman and his friends superpowers, heartbreak quickly turns into a quest for revenge! Betrayed by his best friend over a girl, Stickman discovers he can morph into any shape imaginable. Now, he’s ready to use his new abilities to create chaos and keep the pair apart. Dive into this action-packed story filled with unique animations, clever payback strategies, and endless creativity!
games.instructions: Use a computer mouse to control the game. If you have a mobile device, then use a stylus or a finger. It is necessary to watch the story animation and choose a way to punish the Stickman. You need to click on the buttons to see all the punishments of the Stickman.

games.description: Color Race Obby is an exciting game inspired by Roblox and Obby. Compete with players online on a field of colored blocks. Enter the race and become the champion! Join the fun!
games.instructions: Your goal is to run to the finish line. Watch carefully what color will be next and have time to run to the block of this color. Controls on the computer: W,A,S,D - move the character Space - jump Mouse movement - camera movement Tab - show cursor Controls on the phone: Left joystick - move the character Right button - jump Swipe on the screen - camera movement

games.description: Spinning Uia Uia Cat Bricker is a fun and addictive brick-breaking game where a lively cat motivates you with cheerful meows. Your goal is to clear all the bricks without dropping the ball. As you break more bricks, the cat gets even more excited, dancing and playing around. With colorful graphics and dynamic gameplay, this game offers a delightful experience for players of all ages. Stay sharp and keep up!
games.instructions: Play with mouse.

games.description: In Super Cloner 3D, you are a unique super cloner on a mission to infiltrate dangerous environments. Use your cloning powers to escape traps, kill enemies, and accomplish secret missions.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Dynamic and exciting! Choose the game mode! Complete missions and pass all levels! Levels differ in color palettes and falling elements. Interact with the objects appearing on the game screen, which complicate the process of the game. After accumulating enough pieces, unlock the game type “Infinity”! Choose your favorite level and accumulate as many pieces as possible to beat your opponents!
games.instructions: The control is simple - move the pieces at the bottom of the tracks to match the falling elements and complete the missions on each level. Before the game, choose the appropriate game mode by speed. Be careful, there may be objects on the screen that you need to interact with by clicking on them. To switch the type of game, use the button with the image of a castle. Change the language, disable music and sound effects - in the game settings.

games.description: Simple baseball game with fun, cartoony players and easy one-click controls. It’s fast to learn and fun to play! Unlike other baseball games, the action doesn’t stop after you hit the ball. You need to decide when to run, move to the next base, and try to score runs. It’s all about timing and quick decisions. Pick one of the best baseball countries and try to win the championship. The game keeps the excitement of baseball but with simple rules, so anyone can enjoy it.
games.instructions: Tap anywhere to swing the bat. When your player reaches the base, tap him to run to the next base.

games.description: Unscrew Wood Puzzle: Screw Jam is an engaging puzzle game that combines logic, strategy, and dexterity in a tactile experience. Players are challenged to solve intricate puzzles involving bolts, nuts, and screws. With hundreds of unique levels, this game provides a blend of relaxation and mental stimulation, perfect for casual gamers and puzzle enthusiasts alike. The beautifully designed wooden and metallic elements create a visually appealing and satisfying gameplay experience.
games.instructions: - Objective: Unscrew bolts and unblock pieces to solve puzzles. - Controls: Tap, drag, and pinch to rotate screws, move pieces, and zoom in/out. - Gameplay: Unscrew in the correct sequence to clear obstacles and complete the level. - Tips: Plan your moves and focus on interlocking mechanisms to avoid getting stuck.-

games.description: Building on the classic Vex experience, VEX X3M2 introduces intense levels packed with new hazards and mechanics. New features like kite gliding let you soar over gaps, while teleportation portals help you navigate tricky sections. Floating platforms and shifting obstacles keep you on your toes, making every race an unpredictable thrill ride.
